# GenAi — Full-Stack Project Documentation

> An AI-powered interview preparation platform built with **Express + MongoDB** (Backend) and **React + Vite** (Frontend). Features JWT cookie-based auth, Gemini AI–generated interview reports with technical/behavioral questions, skill gap analysis, a day-by-day preparation roadmap, and AI-generated resume PDF downloads.

